<style>
    .rr_running{
        background-color:green;
    }
    .rr_wait{
        background-color:yellow;
    }    
    .br1 {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
  font-size:2px;
  line-height: 2px;
}
.line18{
    line-height:18px;
}
button span{
    line-height:18px;
}
span{
    line-height:18px;
}
</style>
<script>
    
var f1 = function(){    
    const element = document.documentElement; // 获取整个文档的元素
 
    if (element.requestFullscreen) { // 标准写法
      element.requestFullscreen();
    } else if (element.mozRequestFullScreen) { // Firefox 浏览器
      element.mozRequestFullScreen();
    } else if (element.webkitRequestFullscreen) { // Chrome 和 Safari
      element.webkitRequestFullscreen();
    } else if (element.msRequestFullscreen) { // IE11
      element.msRequestFullscreen();
    }
}

var f2 = function(){
    if (document.exitFullscreen) { // 标准写法
    document.exitFullscreen();
    } else if (document.mozCancelFullScreen) { // Firefox 浏览器
      document.mozCancelFullScreen();
    } else if (document.webkitExitFullscreen) { // Chrome 和 Safari
      document.webkitExitFullscreen();
    } else if (document.msExitFullscreen) { // IE11
      document.msExitFullscreen();
    }
}

var switch_full = 0;
var f3 = function(){
    if(switch_full==0){
        f1();
        switch_full = 1;
    }
    else{
        f2();
        switch_full = 0;
    }
}
    
</script>
<button onclick="f3()" style='height:46px;background-color:rgb(0,148,206);border: 0px;border-radius: 3px;'>屏</button>
